Package morphoide

Class Morphoide

java.lang.Object
morphoide.Morphoide
public class Morphoide extends Object
Morphoide it is a static class to handle the instance in a more accessible way that works with static methods easy to instantiate and use with different functionalities, routine, transformations, mathematical operations and more
